  "texts": [
    "The model achieves an accuracy of 93.10% on ISIC 2016, 87.50% on ISIC 2017 and 96.60% on ISIC 2018.",
    "Panthakkan et al.",
    "[46] proposed a concatenated Xception-ResNet50 (X-R50) model that classifies various skin malignancies.",
    "The effectiveness of the proposed strategy is compared to innovative transfer learning techniques.",
    "Deep CNN is used as a standard to examine other models."
  ]
